    "Oversized rounded corners (>16px on containers)",
    "Pill overload (buttons + cards + badges all pill-shaped)",
    "Glassmorphism as default aesthetic",
    "Soft corporate gradients on headers",
    "Generic dark SaaS layout with no brand identity",
    "Decorative sidebar blobs",
    "Control-room cosplay (dark + neon == production app)",
    "Serif headline + system sans body hack",
    "3-equal-card grid as hero feature section",
    "Centered everything layout",
    "Ghost buttons as primary CTAs",
    "Auto-playing media without user activation",
    "Icon-only navigation without text labels",
    "Emoji in UI (content only is acceptable)"
